sentences.sentence: There is now a black swirly animation when a spell is resisted.
sentences.translation: 当法术被抵抗的时候有一个黑色旋涡形的效果。

sentences.sentence: The point of the CAPTCHA is that reading those swirly letters is something that computers aren't very good at.
sentences.translation: 该测试的重点在于，对于计算机来说，它们不善于辨识这些纠结的字母。

sentences.sentence: Well if it is from a swirly, there something I can do. Okay, circle, circle, dot, dot, now you have a cootie shot!
sentences.translation: 如果是因为这个的话，我倒有个办法。圈，圈，点，点，虱子不再烦扰你！
